column5: any suggestions where my brother can leave his car for 4 days? It's time for our annual Montreal River/lady Evelyn walleye trip.  He is coming in from Ottawa and I from Durham.  Safe in the Walmart parking lot?
Drive the extra little distance to Sturgeon Falls and you can park it in my yard
As long as his wife isn't tracking it... he couldn't probably park it at Fanny's !
PM me and I will help you out. I have room in my driveway and I am only a minute from the bypass / Fisher St intersection.
